{"type": "article", "id": 21416, "title": "邮票和龙舌兰", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-28T07:32:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061537345tynSKor6g4zIkA3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一瓶龙舌兰酒，邮票图案以拼贴的方式贴在了瓶子上。外面的牛皮纸包装也盖上了邮戳，附上了一封明信片，就像是一封邮件，勾起人们怀旧的浪漫情绪。Sin remitente 可以理解为匿名情书，设计者想表现出一种情节而不是商业的标签，发件者可以是邮票上的任何自然景观，他们指向了酒的产地。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150944AGNRQUtDoSFkiT6r.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150944oPKYe2MtAXUEdlfg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"648\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150945YVCJUvc9Hm2ynQw4.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"648\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509465ZFdl6hNDBtQWLbe.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.31759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}